        "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/ccsdk-sli-maven-verify-master-mvn36-openjdk11/464/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/ccsdk-sli-maven-verify-master-mvn36-openjdk11/464",
